            rdfs:label "No. 83b. Asia -- No. 84 b. Africa -- No. 85 b. North America -- No. 86 b. South America -- No. 87 b. Australia -- No. 100b The World (Mercator's Projection) -- No. 101b. Europe -- No. 102b. Asia -- No. 103b. Africa -- No. 105b. South America -- No. 106b. Australiasia and the Philippines -- No. 111b. Europe (central and southern parts) -- No. 113b. The Mediterranean World -- No. 114b. The Baltic Lands -- No. 115b. Eastern Mediterranean and Balkan Region -- No. 121b. England -- No. 122b. Scotland -- No. 123b. Ireland -- No. 124b. France and the Netherlands -- No. 216b. Austro-Hungary and the Danube Valley -- No. 127 b. Russia -- No. 128b. Spain -- No. 130b. Greece and Aegean Sea -- No. 131b. Greece (Continental) -- No. 134b. The Roman Empire -- No. 135b. The Eastern World (from Greece and Egypt to India) -- No. 138b. Palestine -- No. 140b. Egypt -- No. 143b. Ancient Athens -- No. 148 b. India -- No. 149 b. Eastern China and Japan -- No. 170b. Gulf of Mexico, Central America, and Panama -- No. 171b. Mexico and Southwestern United States -- No. 172b. The West Indies -- No. 173b Dominion of Canada -- No. 177b. Eastern United States -- No. 178b. The Mississippi Valley -- No. 179b. Pacific Coast of U. S. -- No. 185b. New England -- No. 186b. New England Colonies -- No. 187b. Middle Atlantic States -- No. 188b. Southern States -- No. 189b. Southern Atlantic Coast of U. S. -- No. 190b. Mississippi Valley. Northern Section -- No. 191b. Mississippi Valley, Northeastern Section -- No. 192b. Mississippi Valley. Northwestern Section -- No. 193b. Mississippi Valley. Southern Section -- No. 194b. Virginia, Maryland and Delaware -- No. 195b. Middle Atlantic Colonies -- No. 229b. California and Nevada -- No. 231b. Connecticut -- No. 232b. Cuba -- No. 239b. Illinois -- No.247b. Massachusetts -- No.248b. Michigan -- No.258b. New York State -- No. 265 b. Pennsylvania -- No. 266b. The Philippines -- No.273b. Texas." ] ;
